  title `Repeals and Savings.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00057_195030_1517807327422&sectionId=27007&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00057_195030_1517807327422
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `Section 7 of the Delhi Laws Act, 1912 (13 of 1912), the Ajmer Merwara`
  line `(Extension of Laws) Act, 1947 (52 of 1947), and any law which immediately ^1`
  line `[before the coming into`
  line `force of any Act or Ordinance extended by this Act to any of the States of Manipur, Tripura and Vindhya`
  line `Pradesh is in force in that State and corresponds to the Act or Ordinance as so extended], are hereby`
  line `repealed:`
  line
  line `Provided that the repeal shall not affect—`
  line
  line `(a) the previous operations of any such law, or`
  line
  line `(b) any penalty, forfeiture or punishment incurred in respect of any offence committed against`
  line `any such law; or`
  line
  line `(c) any investigation, legal proceeding or remedy in respect of any such penalty, forfeiture or`
  line punishment,
  line
  line `and any such investigation, legal proceeding or remedy may be instituted, continued or enforced, and any`
  line `such penalty, forfeiture or punishment may be imposed as if this Act had not been passed:`
  line
  line `Provided further that, subject to the preceding proviso, anything done or any action taken, including`
  line `any appointment or delegation made, notification, order, instruction or direction issued, rule, regulation,`
  line `form, bye-law or scheme framed, certificate, patent, permit or licence granted or registration effected,`
  line `under such law shall be deemed to have been done or taken under section 2 or, as the case may be, under`
  line `the corresponding provision of the Act or Ordinance ^2`
  line `[as extended] to the State by section 3, and shall`
  line `continue in force accordingly, unless and until superseded by anything done or any action taken under the`
  line `said section 2 or, as the case may be, under the said Act or Ordinance.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by s. 3, ibid., for certain words (w.e.f. 1-1-1957).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 68 of 1956, s. 3, for "as now extended" (w.e.f. 1-1-1957).`
